  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 76450be456617df4b8ac569b8d5347be, type: 3}
  description: "An Giang l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\u1ED3ng
    b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng C\u1EEDu Long, n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi c\u1EA3nh quan
    thi\xEAn nhi\xEAn \u0111a d\u1EA1ng v\xE0 n\u1EC1n v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c
    s\u1EAFc. T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt nh\u01B0
    th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Ch\xE2u \u0110\u1ED1c, N\xFAi Sam v\xE0 Mi\u1EBFu B\xE0 Ch\xFAa
    X\u1EE9 \u2013 n\u01A1i thu h\xFAt \u0111\xF4ng \u0111\u1EA3o du kh\xE1ch v\xE0
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi h\xE0nh h\u01B0\u01A1ng m\u1ED7i n\u0103m. Ngo\xE0i ra, An Giang
    c\xF2n n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi c\xE1c c\xE1nh \u0111\u1ED3ng l\xFAa r\u1ED9ng
    l\u1EDBn, h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng s\xF4ng ng\xF2i phong ph\xFA v\xE0 s\u1EF1 giao
    thoa v\u0103n h\xF3a c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u d\xE2n t\u1ED9c nh\u01B0 Kinh, Khmer
    v\xE0 Ch\u0103m."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EC9nh An Giang s\u1EBD s\xE1p nh\u1EADp v\u1EDBi t\u1EC9nh Ki\xEAn
    Giang, v\xE0 t\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1/7/2025, t\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi s\u1EBD mang t\xEAn
    l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh An Giang v\u1EDBi trung t\xE2m ch\xEDnh tr\u1ECB - h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh
    \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i TP Long Xuy\xEAn."
